---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="策划项目 | Fon">
  <div class="prose max-w-none">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">策划项目</h1>
    <p class="text-base opacity-60 mb-10">Campaign Planning & Event Proposals · 活动策划方案</p>

    <div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">

      <!-- 项目一 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2 mb-2">
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">线下路演策划方案</h2>
              <p class="text-xs opacity-50 mt-0.5">WPS / 金山文档 Pop-up Event</p>
            </div>
            <span class="badge badge-success badge-sm whitespace-nowrap">已落地参考</span>
          </div>
          <div class="divider my-2"></div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-4">
            针对 WPS 金山文档品牌的线下路演活动策划方案，涵盖活动主题策划、现场流程设计、执行细节拆解与推广渠道策略，参考已落地活动改写完成。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">活动策划</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">线下执行</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">品牌推广</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="https://www.kdocs.cn/l/cmgmaYTpJ3hq" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary text-secondary-content">
              查看方案 →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 项目二 -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-2 mb-2">
            <div>
              <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">拆解钢琴品牌体验活动</h2>
              <p class="text-xs opacity-50 mt-0.5">WPS / 金山文档 Piano Deconstruction Event</p>
            </div>
            <span class="badge badge-warning badge-sm whitespace-nowrap">概念方案</span>
          </div>
          <div class="divider my-2"></div>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-4">
            以「拆解钢琴」为核心创意的品牌体验活动策划，将艺术装置与互动体验结合，打造沉浸式品牌场景。因合作方原因未能最终落地，保留完整策划思路与执行框架。
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">创意策划</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">品牌体验</span>
            <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">艺术装置</span>
          </div>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end">
            <a href="https://www.kdocs.cn/l/cbG178mfaIbu" target="_blank" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary text-secondary-content">
              查看方案 →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- 说明 -->
    <section class="not-prose border rounded-xl p-6 opacity-70">
      <h3 class="font-bold mb-2 text-sm">关于这些方案 · About These Proposals</h3>
      <p class="text-sm">
        线下路演方案是根据朋友希望参考的已落地活动改写而成；拆解钢琴方案为原创策划，因合作方原因未能落地。两份方案均完整呈现了从创意提案到执行细节的全流程思路。
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
